{"tid":2044541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"隔離post話美國黑人無被壓迫","createTime":"2020-05-31T07:22:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-31T12:09:33.000Z","uid":74303,"like":27,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"075552e8829dcd5a90120d44ba8f3e28586cda25","tid":2044541,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:22:08.000Z","msg":"隔離post話因為<br />\n1. 美國大學加分俾黑人入學<br />\n2. 美國吹捧黑人hiphop搞到pop and rock死曬<br />\n3. 黑人犯罪率好高<br />\n基於呢三個原因你話人地無被壓迫 完全反映唔到任何事實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地之所以示威一定有佢地嘅原因<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">如果話佢地無被壓迫，咁同藍絲話示威者無端端出嚟搞事有咩分別</span><br />\n<br />\n我地唔係美國人、無喺美國生活過、又唔係黑人<br />\n憑咩討論黑人有無被壓迫<br />\n就好似如果美國人話我地無俾大陸壓迫，我地都會屌啦<br />\n<br />\n人地風頭火勢，我地一係同情show sympathy，一係就唔好出聲唔好理<br />\n到時講錯嘢得罪人地 國際戰線就byebye<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">請大家唔好再討論美國黑人有無被壓迫</span></span>"},{"pid":"6aec862dbcbdce0bb63574ce8baae1089592cad3","tid":2044541,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:22:52.000Z","msg":"美國啲黑人根本冇被壓迫！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2044420\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2044420</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n小心風向撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09675f2bea2599dfa951ac17423a5c9d381fd2ff","tid":2044541,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:23:28.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"136be3472d67cf6cc6dd54348187f130e6865905","tid":2044541,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:24:07.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a8b8a5b0c0c908d240db2c182dbe8f3ed6f81fb2","tid":2044541,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T07:24:39.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"c7a64d864e521499fac046d585684d8032623bf4","tid":2044541,"uid":74303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":